Class Null

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.core.stopwords.AbstractStopwords
      • weka.core.stopwords.Null
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, OptionHandler, StopwordsHandler

    public class Null
extends AbstractStopwords
    Dummy stopwords scheme, always returns false.

    Valid options are: 

     -D
  If set, stopword scheme is run in debug mode and
  may output additional info to the console
